commit_message: Change .gitignore to ignore the .tar.gz installation files
Change defaults for p-val, win sizes and info col
Modify .gitignore to ignore make generated files

Make local window size a parameter in findHotspots.pl

The two local window sizes were previously fixed constants. They are
made parameters now to suit various situations.

Also fixed a bug that takes column 11 as the event column. It is changed
to column 7.
Add whitespaces in README as a test.

Add download files for diffReps
They include an example ChIP-seq dataset, diffReps v1.43 and v1.55.4
installation files. v1.55.4 is the most up-to-date version while
v1.43 is the last known reliable version.
